        <briefdescription>
<para>Updates collider bounds for all applicable entities. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>For each entity with the required components, composes the local transform from translation, rotation, and scale, then applies the parent world transform to compute the final world-space AABB.</para>
